    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 4 players battle it out in multiple rounds of wacky physics-based swordplay, where the losers of each round are granted a selection of random permanent upgrades by their patron god. Amidst the escalating chaos only one player will become the Clumsy Champion, will it be you?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only the losers get upgrades, meaning the power balance is always shifting in this medieval arms race</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics based damage means players can get creative with their upgrade choices and how they approach a fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 3 other friends locally or online (Steam remote play supported)</p></li></ul>",
